    "note": "Scores were tuned for a fixed three-stop private Gapyeong loop with strong scenic and photo fit, high comfort and family fit (private format), and moderate walking. Iconic landmark fit is maxed because all three stops are top-tier Korean tourism brand names. Same-day-flight fit is low because the loop runs 9-10 hours and ends in late afternoon or evening.",
    "duration_hours": 10,
    "stop_count": 3,
    "score_rationale": {
      "scenic_level": "Maxed because all three stops are visually distinct and well-curated.",
      "photo_level": "Maxed because all three are heavy K-drama filming locations with seasonally rotating photo windows.",
      "private_fit": "Direct match: per-vehicle private charter.",
      "family_fit": "Very high because private comfort plus child-friendly stops (rabbits at Nami, Marionettes at Petite France) make it broadly accessible.",
      "rain_fit": "Mid because most walking is outdoor; Petite France indoor halls help but do not cover the full route.",
      "iconic_landmark_fit": "Maxed because the three stops are the most-recognized day-trip combination from Seoul."
    },
